        <updateDate>2020-11-18T14:32:43Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Providing Liquidity for Uncollectible Sales Act of 2020 or as the PLUS Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill allows a new tax credit for the uncollectible accounts receivable of an eligible wholesale distributor. The bill defines an <i>eligible wholesale distributor</i> as any person engaged in the trade or business of selling inventory to a food and beverage establishment that ceases to provide on-premises consumption of food and beverage on or after March 25, 2020, pursuant to an order or recommendation of an applicable governmental authority. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
